abstractContent.text: PREFACE The conference program and organization have been created through the efforts of a large number of people who have given generously of their time and talents.

I especially thank the program committee: Applications Panel: rim Finin Other energetic contributors include Martha Evens and Victor Yngve, who have made it posmble to meet at the University of Chicago; Carole Hafner, who has put together a marvelous collection of exhibits and demonstrations; Lisa Trentham, who has facilitated the necessary communication in a hundred ways; and Norm Sondheimer and Don Walker.
